            </li>
            <li>
              <a href="#about" id="about-link"
                ><span class="icon fa-user">About Us</span></a
              >
            </li>
            <li>
              <a href="#contact" id="contact-link"
                ><span class="icon fa-envelope">Contact</span></a
              >
            </li>
            <li>
              <a href="/logout" id="contact-link"
                ><span class="fas fa-sign-out-alt">Logout</span></a
              >
            </li>
          </ul>
        </nav>
      </div>

      <div class="bottom">
        <!-- Social Icons -->
        <ul class="icons">
          <li>
            <a href="#" class="icon fa-twitter"
              ><span class="label">Twitter</span></a
            >
          </li>
          <li>
            <a href="#" class="icon fa-facebook"
              ><span class="label">Facebook</span></a
            >
          </li>
          <li>
            <a href="#" class="icon fa-instagram"
              ><span class="label">Instagram</span></a
            >
          </li>
        </ul>
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- Main -->
    <div id="main">
      <!-- Intro -->
      <section id="top" class="one dark cover">
        <div class="container">
          <header>
            <h2 class="alt">
              Welcome <strong><%= session.user_fname %></strong>!<br />
              This is a site demo for Pendo <a href="https://www.pendo.io/">pendo.io</a>.
            </h2>
            <p>
              Take a look at what Pendo can do for your<br />
              company and how we can help you make the most of your website.
            </p>
          </header>

          <footer>
            <a href="https://www.pendo.io/customers/" class="button scrolly">Check It Out</a>
          </footer>
        </div>
      </section>

      <!-- Portfolio -->
      <section id="portfolio" class="two">
        <div class="container">
          <header>
            <h2>North Sentinel Island</h2>
          </header>

          <p>
            North Sentinel Island is home to one of the last undiluted
            hunter-and-gatherer societies, a rugged, Manhattan-sized island
            where a few dozen people live trapped in time and in total
            isolation. For decades, India has kept North Sentinel in a museum
            case.
          </p>

          <div class="row">
            <div class="col-4 col-12-mobile">
              <article class="item">
                <a href="#" class="image fit"
                  ><img src="/images/relaxAvatar.jpeg" alt=""
                /></a>
                <header>
                  <h3>Relax</h3>
                </header>
              </article>
              <article class="item">
                <a href="#" class="image fit"
                  ><img src="/images/kayak.jpeg" alt=""
                /></a>
                <header>
                  <h3>Explore</h3>
                </header>
              </article>
            </div>
            <div class="col-4 col-12-mobile">
              <article class="item">
                <a href="#" class="image fit"
                  ><img src="/images/hotel.jpeg" alt=""
                /></a>
                <header>
                  <h3>Sleep</h3>
                </header>
              </article>
              <article class="item">
                <a href="#" class="image fit"
                  ><img src="/images/swim.jpeg" alt=""
                /></a>
                <header>
                  <h3>Swim</h3>
                </header>
              </article>
            </div>
            <div class="col-4 col-12-mobile">
              <article class="item">
                <a href="#" class="image fit"
                  ><img src="/images/girlOnBoat.jpeg" alt=""
                /></a>
                <header>
                  <h3>Tours</h3>
                </header>
              </article>
              <article class="item">
                <a href="#" class="image fit"
                  ><img src="/images/relax.jpeg" alt=""
                /></a>
                <header>
                  <h3>Unwind</h3>
                </header>
              </article>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </section>

      <!-- About Me -->
      <section id="about" class="three">
        <div class="container">
          <header>
            <h2>About Pendo Travel</h2>
          </header>

          <a href="#" class="image featured"
            ><img src="/images/travelPrep.jpeg" alt=""
          /></a>

          <p>
            Started in 2019 by two friends looking to enjoy life. After
            discovering the struggles of seeing the world with limited money and
            resources. We wanted to create a way to make seeing the world as
            pain free as possible.
          </p>
        </div>
      </section>

      <!-- Contact -->
      <section id="contact" class="four">
        <div class="container">
          <header>
            <h2>Contact</h2>
          </header>

          <p>
            We try to do our best to curate the best vacations for you! No need
            to plan anything. If you have any questions, feel free to reach out!
          </p>

          <form method="post" action="#">
            <div class="row">
              <div class="col-6 col-12-mobile">
                <input type="text" name="name" placeholder="Name" />
              </div>
              <div class="col-6 col-12-mobile">
                <input type="text" name="email" placeholder="Email" />
              </div>
              <div class="col-12">
                <textarea name="message" placeholder="Message"></textarea>
              </div>
              <div class="col-12">
                <input type="submit" value="Send Message" />
              </div>
            </div>
          </form>
        </div>
      </section>
    </div>

    <!-- Footer -->
    <div id="footer">
      <!-- Copyright -->
      <ul class="copyright">
        <li>&copy; Pendo Test. All rights reserved.</li>
        <li>Design: Essie Hammadani</li>
      </ul>
    </div>

